Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.23,0:00:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.79,0:00:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.26,0:00:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.19,0:01:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.28,0:01:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rebeca and Otogi\N challenged Varon to a Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.36,0:01:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But up against the mysterious abilities of Varon's Armor Deck, they were defeated in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he aiming for Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the same time, Kaiba is taking his own private plane towards the museum in Florida.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.91,0:01:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the aurora appeared in the sky again and hindered the path ahead with a veil of haze.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Revenging Amelda - The Great Airborne Duel"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The icy waters are so comfortable~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I just soak my feet for a bit,\N the pain should-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's rest here for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't be wasting time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let it bother you. Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} and Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0} should already be close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go ahead first!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You should...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say you ain't afraid of nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But long and soft things are an exception!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we lost control of Duel Monsters, auroras also appeared all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me! Hey! Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go and have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How weird... There's no one onboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Humph! What's the matter, Kaiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you worrying about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This voice is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you finally realized what's going on, Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amelda, where are you?! Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, the cockpit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The plane is set to autopilot mode...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not {\b0}there{\b1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tch... What dumb tricks he's pulling...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you doing? I am over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scumbag...! You'll pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being able to see you again makes me happy, Seto Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amelda!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd the rest of the crew run off to, you lowlife?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no need for people unrelated to our conflict to be in the middle of our battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was never anyone of the sort onboard from the getco.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we have the power of Doma, such a thing is a simple task.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we settle our Duel once and for all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My little brother was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...killed by your company!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Amelda! Your fight against my brother was a mistake to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before that this is {\i1}revenge{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amelda...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what intentions you have...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in a Duel, only the one that is calm and collected can be the victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, only the strong can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother, please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will accept this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:06:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, as if you had a choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba, I'm going to watch as your soul is taken from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and give Miruko peace of mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will go first. Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Science Special Soldier in Defense Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon X-Head Cannon in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Science Special Soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why must Amelda and Big Brother do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Machine Soldier of the Demon World in Defense Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:07:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next I set one card and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Y-Dragon Head in Attack Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Dragon Head, attack Machine Soldier of Demon World!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, I use X-Head Cannon to Direct Attack the player!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one reverse card, ending my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn. Draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of you, Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you can Summon two Monsters in such a short time and give me a Direct Attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you've got much more to show, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if that's the case, then this place will be a little cramped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will need a more spacious room to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... you've drawn that card?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back, Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate this instant!\N The Barrier of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card that has been tainted by everything will awaken the darkness in your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will let you see what both me and my brother saw from Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amelda, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amelda!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Big Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:09:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The plane's altitude has fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:09:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Autopiloting has been deactivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, I can't move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, the control station! Gotta contact the control station!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, you must be connected! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hurry it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be deceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the occult supernatural illusions that Amelda wants me to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, looks like you've woken up, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're awake, get on outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.56,0:11:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our hiding spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this garbage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That ain't garbage! We picked them up from the city streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:12:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many useful things are dropped in the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dennis!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,War?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They drop things like this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna pass those things to our own people protecting the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we can get the enemy outta our city and put an end to this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chess, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, you can play chess?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Yuan? If you're not gonna eat, then go back to the streets and collect some more stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your "collection" is the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get on with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know that all of this is just an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I also know that Amelda wants to use these illusions to waver my thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tony and Dennis both lost their parents in this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not just us. Almost half the kids living in this city are like that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for me, I still have Tony and Dennis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm not lonely at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.64,0:13:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amelda, what do you want me to see here...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, you know how to play chess, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That chess board belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna play me, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This big one is the King, and this is the Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I will move this here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\b0}Again{\b1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're just as\N good as always, big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn now, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're playing it like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I will play like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That came from the Church!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tony! Dennis!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tony! Dennis!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, it's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tony! Dennis!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all just a deceiving illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't believe in this, Amelda!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,End this dirty trick immediatly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amelda!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amelda!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuan...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You actually created such a ridiculously fake illusion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was not {\i1}fake{\i0}. That was based off of real events.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That kid died after being struck by military fire soon after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this city, such a sight is not rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My little brother, Miruko, also died like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let us continue with the game, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used KC-1 Clayton and the Trap Card on my field, Tank Corp,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to Summon three Tokens and attack your Y-Dragon Head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KC-1 Clayton's ATK will increase by 500 for every Token on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, your Life will decrease by 2000 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, I set one card face-down and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba, it's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate a Magic Card!\N Resurrection of the Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will revive Y-Dragon Head and next, I Summon Z-Metal Caterpiller!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will combine all three - X-Head Cannon, Y-Dragon Head and Z-Metal Caterpiller!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Special Summon XYZ-Dragon Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate XYZ-Dragon Cannon's Special Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By discarding one card from my hand, I can destroy one of my opponent's cards on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:19:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the Tokens have disappared, KC-1 Clayton's ATK will go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, I will use XYZ-Dragon Cannon to attack KC-1 Clayton!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate the enemy! Go, XYZ Hyper Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel your anguish and sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what happens to us in the midst of war!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm just battling during my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a "Duel"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, this is {\i1}reality{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, I am still praying from that war.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:20:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am praying that all weapons will disappear from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am praying for a peaceful world with no war to become a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is not possible at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are people like Gozaburo Kaiba crawling all over this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then... and now as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.19,0:20:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapons will not disappear and humans will never stop fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, this kind of world might as well be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And from the scraps of "zero", a world with no war can be built!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized this one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I realized this because I was {\i1}awoken{\i0} by Doma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And for that aim, I will need your soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:20:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the middle of a match here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my next turn, I am going to draw out my key card that will send you to your grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to use that card to take your soul away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all for the sake of returning the world to zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.18,0:22:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.54,0:22:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.15,0:22:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.22,0:22:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.98,0:22:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.88,0:22:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.03,0:23:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.55,0:23:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.62,0:23:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of Amelda's attack, Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s plane has lost control and is decreasing in altitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0} can't regain control by himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.05,0:23:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But unless Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} beats Amelda in this Duel, he can't escape from the barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then Amelda finally plays his trump card!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.10,0:23:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that Monster...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.81,0:23:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.52,0:23:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sky Devil Fortress Ziggurat"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.94,0:23:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
